00:04:42.099 --> 00:04:46.689
encoder and a small computer which actually
controls the motor and the motor controls

00:04:46.689 --> 00:04:52.419
signals coming through this, three wire cable
which provides power and also the velocity

00:04:52.419 --> 00:04:53.330
command signal.

